Package com.graph

Class Graph

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.graph.Graph
  • class Graph
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used for building a graph. The graph is based on a adjacency list of elements of type Node. The output received after certain commands is written in an output file named "map.out".
